Nkosinathi Phiwayinkosi Thamsanqa Nhleko, Onye a maara nke ọma dị ka Nathi Nhleko، Bụ onye bụbu Minista ndị uwe ojii South Africa. Nhleko jere ozi na nzuko omeiwu dị ka Onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Portfolio na Ọrụ Ọha na Nchịkwa, onye isi oche nke African National Congress (ANC)
Tinyere onye isi ụtarị nke ANC, na onye otu Kọmitii Ọrụ Ikpe.
